    Expression, HasImports

    public final class ToBoolFlux
extends AbstractParametrizedFlux
    Convert a value to a bool. See SPEC.

    Example 

     Flux flux = Flux
     .from("telegraf")
     .filter(and(measurement().equal("mem"), field().equal("used")))
     .toBool();

    Jakub Bednar (bednar@github) (25/06/2018 15:57)
